## Phase 5: Launch Preparation (~2 weeks)

**Goal**: Validated, monitored production deployment.

### Tasks

| # | Task | Priority | Est. Time |
|---|---|---|---|
| 5.1 | **Closed beta test** with 10-20 users on staging | 🔴 Critical | 7 days |
| 5.2 | **Verify Sentry error reporting** with intentional test exceptions | 🟠 High | 2 hours |
| 5.3 | **Verify Firebase push notifications** end-to-end | 🟠 High | 1 day |
| 5.4 | **Performance profiling**: Test on low-end Android device, check for jank in the 22KB learning dashboard | 🟠 High | 2 days |
| 5.5 | **Localization check**: Verify `AppLocalizations` works for target languages | 🟡 Medium | 1 day |
| 5.6 | **Asset completion**: Ensure all Codemaster Odyssey game assets are in place (you mentioned you're working on this) | 🟠 High | Ongoing |
| 5.7 | **App Store / Play Store preparation**: Screenshots, descriptions, privacy policy, age rating | 🟡 Medium | 2 days |
| 5.8 | **Production deployment**: Build release APK/AAB with correct `--dart-define` keys, deploy to Play Store | 🔴 Critical | 1 day |

### Exit Criteria
- [ ] Zero crashes in 7-day beta
- [ ] Sentry captures and reports errors correctly
- [ ] APK size < 100MB
- [ ] Play Store listing approved

