| Phase | Duration | Effort | Impact on Score |
|---|---|---|---|
| Phase 1: Code Hygiene | ~1 week | Low | 35 → 45 |
| Phase 2: Critical Tests | ~2 weeks | High | 45 → 65 |
| Phase 3: Security Verification | ~1.5 weeks | High | 65 → 75 |
| Phase 4: CI/CD Hardening | ~1 week | Medium | 75 → 82 |
| Phase 5: Launch Prep | ~2 weeks | Medium | 82 → 90 |

**Total estimated time: ~7.5 weeks** from today to production-ready.

